text: Saint-Leu-la-Forêt is a commune. It is in Île-de-France in the Val-d'Oise department in north France. In 2019, 16,130 people lived there. The commune is in the northwestern suburbs of Paris, from the center. == Twin towns == Saint- Leu-la-Forêt is twinned with: * Wendlingen am Neckar, Germany * Culcheth, England, United Kingdom == References == Category:Communes in Val-d'Oise
title: Saint-Leu-la-Forêt
